        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You are physiologically compelled to move. Staying in the same place for too long causes you to feel intense fear and even hyperventilate. Unless you are in a moving vehicle, as long as you are @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Immobilized] you are @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Frightened]{Frightened 1} and you do not lower your frightened condition at the end of your turns. Once you are no longer immobilized, reduce your frightened condition by 1.</p>"
